      "citation_id": "[CITATION_2]",
      "span_text": "In addition, [CITATION_2] found that people can reduce the guilt evoked by consuming self-indulgent items by engaging in a kind behavior toward someone else (i.e. giving a promotional item to a friend rather than keeping it for themselves)."
